1 135.715. 1. The cumulative amount of tax credits that
2 may be allocated to all taxpayers contributing to
3 educational assistance organizations in the first year of
4 the program shall not exceed twenty-five million dollars.
5 2. The [state treasurer] department of elementary and
6 secondary education shall limit the number of educational
14

7 assistance organizations that are certified to administer
